summary: This is an email exchange from October 15, 2019, regarding logistical arrangements for a meeting with Epstein victims in West Palm Beach (WPB). The sender confirms securing a conference room for the meeting, which is part of an ongoing victim outreach effort.

events.title: Epstein Victim Meeting Coordination
events.description: An email exchange confirms the arrangement of a conference room for a meeting with Epstein victims in West Palm Beach (WPB). The meeting is scheduled for the following day (October 16, 2019).

keyFacts: The document is an email dated October 15, 2019, concerning logistical support for a meeting with Epstein victims.
The meeting was to take place in West Palm Beach (WPB) on October 16, 2019.
The email indicates an ongoing effort by an unspecified party to meet with victims of Jeffrey Epstein.
The sender had already secured a conference room for the victim meeting by the time of the email.
